<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>New York Office</p>
<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>Wachsman PR is seeking an accomplished Senior Account Executive for its New York office. The Senior Account Executive will be responsible for all aspects of day-to-day account execution, reporting to an Account Supervisor. They will assist in the planning and execution of PR campaigns while developing relationships with US and international reporters. Possible travel may be required.</p>
<p>Duties:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Planning and executing PR campaigns
</li>
<li>
Managing day-to-day internal and external communications on behalf of clients
</li>
<li>
Drafting, editing and reviewing press materials
</li>
<li>
Dealing with enquiries from press, clients, new business and external organizations
</li>
<li>
Issuing press releases and pitching to reporters both within the US and internationally
</li>
<li>
Conducting one-on-one client engagement
</li>
<li>
Undertaking industry research and generating story ideas and angles
</li>
<li>
Developing and maintain relationships with media to secure and grow coverage
</li>
<li>
Conducting meetings with clients and potential new business
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>
Managing, supporting, and training junior team members.
</li>
</ul>
<p>The successful applicant will have: </p>
<ul>
<li>
At least 3 year&rsquo;s PR agency experience.
</li>
<li>
Exceptional work ethic and motivated to excel in a fast-paced environment.
</li>
<li>
Outstanding written and verbal communication with an interest in finance and technology.
</li>
<li>
Track record of securing media coverage and experience in developing relationships with reporters.
</li>
<li>
Ability to think strategically when developing PR campaigns.
</li>
<li>
Excellent organizational skills with exceptional attention to detail
</li>
<li>
Experience in and ability to work well in a team.
</li>
<li>
Experience in and ability to lead junior staff effectively
</li>
<li>
Strong interpersonal skills.
</li>
</ul>
<p>All candidates please send your CV and an original and tailored cover letter with salary expectations to&nbsp;<a href="mailto:newyork@wachsmanpr.com" target="_blank">newyork@wachsmanpr.com</a>
&nbsp;</p>